description.fr: {CharacterName:596} retourne à la chasse aux Shushus, en direction de l'{WorldZone:3}.
description.en: {CharacterName:596}'s heading out Shushu hunting again, this time on {WorldZone:3}.
description.es: {CharacterName:596} vuelve a la caza de fab'huritus, en dirección de la {WorldZone:3}.
description.de: {CharacterName:596} begibt sich wieder auf Shushu-Jagd. Weiter geht’s zur {WorldZone:3}!
description.pt: {CharacterName:596} retorna à caça aos Shushus, agora rumo à {WorldZone:3}.

descriptionFinished.fr: {CharacterName:596} a de nouveau rencontré {Summoning:590}, le Shushu fuyard précédemment éliminé. Le mystère reste entier\_: comment est-ce possible\_?
descriptionFinished.en: {CharacterName:596}'s run into {Summoning:590} again, but he'd already eliminated the cowardly Shushu before. How is that possible? It's a mystery.
descriptionFinished.es: {CharacterName:596} se ha vuelto a encontrar con {Summoning:590}, el fab'huritu fugitivo que había eliminado anteriormente. Es todo un misterio: ¿cómo es posible?
descriptionFinished.de: {CharacterName:596} ist erneut auf {Summoning:590} getroffen, den wendigen Shushu, den er eigentlich längst erledigt hatte. Es ist kaum zu fassen: Wie ist das möglich?
descriptionFinished.pt: {CharacterName:596} encontrou {Summoning:590} mais uma vez, o Shushu fujão que já havia sido eliminado. O mistério continua: como é possível?
